snippet.title: Terror attack at army base in Jammu And Kashmir's Uri

localized.description:
At least four terrorists have attacked an army administrative base in Jammu and Kashmir's Uri, which is near the Line of Control. A gun battle is on. The injured have been airlifted to an Army hospital in state capital Srinagar, about 70 km away.

Watch more videos: http://www.ndtv.com/video?yt
